<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<body>
    <div class="header-banner">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="banner">
                <div class="indent">
                    <h2 class="indent-left margin-bot" style="margin-left:80px;">Tatil & Seyahat Blogum</h2>
                    <div class="banner-left">
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/glass.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Restoranlar</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/flight.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Ucuslar</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/group.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Yapilacak Seyler</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/key.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Arac Kiralama</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="header_bottom_right_images">

                        <div class="slider" style="width:650px;height:365px;">
                            <ul class="rslides" id="slider1">
                                @foreach (var x in Model)
                                {
                                    <li><img src="@x.BlogImage" alt="" style="width:690px; height:365px;"></li>
                                    @*<li><img src="~/web/images/img2.jpg" alt=""></li>
                                        <li><img src="~/web/images/img3.jpg" alt=""></li>
                                        <li><img src="~/web/images/img4.jpg" alt=""></li>*@
                                }
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class"content">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="con-top">
                    <h3>Tatil Seyahat Bloguma Hosgeldiniz!</h3>
                    <p>Bu projeyi Mayis 2020 tarihinde baslatip Haziran 2020 tarihinde ana sayfa duzenlemelerine getirdik. Gezip gordugum yerleri sizlerle paylasmak icin kodlamasini tamamen kendim yaptigim mvc5 uzerine kurulu dinamik bir web projesi gelistirdik. Hem Turkiye`den hem yurt disindan gezip gordugum yerleri blog yazilari olarak sizlerle paylasma niyetindeyim. Umuyorum ki yazdiklarimi begenirsiniz, keyifli okumalar, saglikli gunler.</p>
                </div>
                @Html.Action("Partial1", "Default")
                <div class="grids">
                    <div class="box1">
                        @Html.Action("Partial2","Default")
                        @Html.Action("Partial3","Default")
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
